#. module: mail
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:mail.field_mail_mail__scheduled_date
msgid "If set, the queue manager will send the email after the date. If not set, the email will be send as soon as possible. Unless a timezone is specified, it is considered as being in UTC timezone."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າຕັ້ງໄວ້, ຕົວຈັດການຄິວຈະສົ່ງອີເມລຫຼັງຈາກວັນທີນີ້. ຖ້າບໍ່ໄດ້ຕັ້ງ, ອີເມລຈະຖືກສົ່ງໂດຍໄວທີ່ສຸດ. ຫາກບໍ່ໄດ້ລະບຸເຂດ"
"ເວລາ, ຈະຖືວ່າຢູ່ໃນເຂດເວລາ UTC."

#. module: mail
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:mail.field_mail_template__scheduled_date
msgid "If set, the queue manager will send the email after the date. If not set, the email will be send as soon as possible. You can use dynamic expression."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າຕັ້ງໄວ້, ຕົວຈັດການຄິວຈະສົ່ງອີເມລຫຼັງຈາກວັນທີນີ້. ຖ້າບໍ່ໄດ້ຕັ້ງ, ອີເມລຈະຖືກສົ່ງໂດຍໄວທີ່ສຸດ. ທ່ານສາມາດໃຊ້ສຳ"
"ນວນແບບໄດນາມິກໄດ້."

#. module: mail
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:mail.field_mail_alias__alias_bounced_content
