#. module: mail
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:mail.field_mail_alias__alias_force_thread_id
msgid "Optional ID of a thread (record) to which all incoming messages will be attached, even if they did not reply to it. If set, this will disable the creation of new records completely."
msgstr ""
"ID ທາງເລືອກຂອງເທຣດ (ບັນທຶກ) ທີ່ຂໍ້ຄວາມຂາເຂົ້າທັງໝົດຈະຖືກຄັດຕິດໄວ້, ເຖິງແມ່ນວ່າພວກເຂົາຈະບໍ່ໄດ້ຕອບກັບກໍ"
"ຕາມ. ຖ້າຕັ້ງໄວ້, ມັນຈະປິດການສ້າງບັນທຶກໃໝ່ໂດຍສິ້ນເຊີງ."

#. module: mail
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:mail.field_mail_notification__mail_mail_id
